OL,3,CPilgrims face extreme heat during
OL,4,Cworld's largest annual peaceful
OL,5,Cgathering
OL,7,FBy ITV News Producer Zahra Manji
OL,9,FEvery year, millions of Shia Muslims -
OL,10,Falongside some of other faiths from
OL,11,Faround the globe - make the journey to
OL,12,FIraq to participate in what makes up
OL,13,Fthe world's largest annual peaceful
OL,14,Fgathering, known as Arbaeen.
OL,16,FThe number of pilgrims has been
OL,17,Fsteadily rising to at least 22
OL,18,Fmillion. In comparison, almost 2
OL,19,Fmillion pilgrims participated in the
OL,20,FHajj to Mecca, Saudi Arabia.
