OL,3,CPilgrims face extreme heat during
OL,4,Cworld's largest annual peaceful
OL,5,Cgathering
OL,7,FThis year, temperatures have reached
OL,8,Fextreme heights topping 50C, with
OL,9,Fpilgrims being cooled down with
OL,10,Fsprayed water during their walk to
OL,11,FKarbala.
OL,13,FWhy do people commemorate Arbaeen?
OL,15,FLiterally meaning '40' in Arabic, the
OL,16,FDay of Arbaeen marks 40 days after the
OL,17,FDay of Ashura, the day Imam Hussain,
OL,18,Fthe grandson of the Prophet Muhammed,
OL,19,Fand his family were martyred in what
OL,20,Fis now the city of Karbala, Iraq.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
