OL,7,FHussain and his family refused to
OL,8,Fsubmit to the oppressive regime at the
OL,9,Ftime.
OL,11,FPilgrims believe Hussain's message to
OL,12,Fbe a timeless one and just as those
OL,13,Fwho lived in the seventh century were
OL,14,Finspired by their stand, so are the
OL,15,Fmillions today who pay homage to
OL,16,FHussain and mourn his death.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
