OL,7,FThe Day of Arbaeen is also said to be
OL,8,Fthe day on which Hussain's family
OL,9,Freturned to the land of Karbala, to
OL,10,Fproperly bid farewell to the fallen
OL,11,Fheroes and finally grieve for their
OL,12,Floved ones.
OL,14,FIt is a spiritual experience for
OL,15,Fpilgrims, and is made even more
OL,16,Fspecial by the connections they form
OL,17,Fwith the city's hosts as Iraqi locals
OL,18,Fopen their homes and hearts to
OL,19,Fvisitors.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
