OL,7,FThe ancient city of Karbala transforms
OL,8,Fduring the period, with friends,
OL,9,Ffamilies and elders alike united under
OL,10,Fred, green and black banners, while
OL,11,Fdressed in 'mourning' black.
OL,13,FWhat takes place during the pilgrimage?
OL,15,FA walk of 80km takes place from the
OL,16,Fcity of Najaf to Karbala, where
OL,17,Fpilgrims of all ages, nationalities
OL,18,Fand physical abilities travel between
OL,19,Fthe shrines of the Prophet's son in
OL,20,Flaw Imam Ali and the Prophet's
OL,21,Fgrandson Hussain.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
