OL,7,FEvery year, Arbaeen is marked with
OL,8,Fprocessions and religious services at
OL,9,FShia Muslim mosques across the world
OL,10,Fto remember the story of Prophet
OL,11,FMuhammed's grandson, his family and
OL,12,Fhis companions.
OL,14,FDr Ammar Nakshawani, director of the
OL,15,FProphet Muhammad Institute for Islamic
OL,16,FStudies, has been to Iraq during
OL,17,FArbaeen for the last 16 years.
OL,19,FHe told ITV News: "It really is a
OL,20,Fspiritual journey and a wonderful
OL,21,Fatmosphere".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
