OL,7,FDr Nakshawani said Imam Hussain is "a
OL,8,Fdescendant of Abraham and therefore
OL,9,Fresonates with many non-Muslims too".
OL,11,F"There are unbelievable lessons to be
OL,12,Flearned," Dr Ammar Nakshawani says
OL,14,FProfessor in theology, Dr Chris Hewer,
OL,15,Fexperienced his first Arbaeen in
OL,16,FKarbala last year. "We had in these 25
OL,17,Fmillion people not just Muslims, but
OL,18,FChristians, Jews, Hindus and those of
OL,19,Fno faith at all".
OL,21,FWhy is so little know about Arbaeen?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
