OL,7,FOnly 10-15% of the world's 1.8 billion
OL,8,FMuslims are Shia and therefore Arbaeen
OL,9,Fis not widely known.
OL,11,FProfessor in Theology and Religion at
OL,12,Fthe University of Oxford, Justin
OL,13,FJones, said "The Hajj is better known
OL,14,Fas it is obligatory on all Muslims,
OL,15,Fwhereas Shia traditions are less well
OL,16,Fknown because popular knowledge is
OL,17,Fshaped much more by Sunni Islam".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
